 full spectrum of minerals like:\r\nMagnesium,\r\nZinc,\r\nSelenium,\r\nChromium,\r\nManganese,\r\nGermanium,\r\nand it is rich in Iron.</td>\r\n<td class="box_bg_color_04">\r\n<h2>Others</h2>\r\nPhytopigments and Antioxidants:\r\n-Carotenoids\r\n-Phycocyanin, Chlorophyl\r\n-Xanthophylls, Zeaxanthin\r\n\r\nFatty acids &amp; Enzymes:\r\n-Gamma Linolenic (GLA)\r\n-Omega 3 &amp; 6\r\n-Essential Linoleic\r\n-SOD Superoxide Dismutase</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table><!--:-->', '<!--:en-->What is Spirulina?<!--:-->', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '24-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-15 09:39:16', '2013-11-15 09:39:16', '', 24, 'http://localhost/spiralps.ch/uncategorized/24-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
