.png" width="229" height="164" />Yannick is a young 38-year old exiled mountain dweller, married and father of a charming daughter. Having no running water in his country of origin, Yannick started many years ago on a long trip. He left the snowy peaks of his "Chablais Savoyard", on foot, swam across the Lake of Geneva, and settled in what he calls "a civilized country".\r\n\r\nYannick is passionate about biology and communication, as Frederic would say, "He never stops talking". Yannick loves nature and it is why, quite naturally, that he became a fan of Spirulina from the very start.\r\n\r\n[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[one_half]\r\n<h2><span style="color: #339966;">Frederic Dubois</span></h2>\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-148" alt="Fred" src="http://localhost/spiralps.ch/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Fred.png" width="229" height="164" />Frederic is a young 43-year old, married father of two nice boys. Frederic is a big fan of mountaineering and nature. He is an active member of the Swiss Alpine Club and is responsible for a mountain hut, perched at 2600m, in the heart of the Alps.\r\n\r\nAlthough Frederic tried to convince Yannick to be content with growing Spirulina beside the mountain hut, making drinks, and waiting for customers... Yannick was quick to point out that it would not be profitable in the long run.\r\n\r\nTherefore Frederic, the Doctor of the team, (not a medical doctor, he is afraid of blood - but an eco-chemist with a doctorate), made it his goal, to bring his scientific knowledge to bear, on better serving the entire world with their more healthful, fresh Spirulina beverage.\r\n\r\n[/one_half]<!--:-->', '<!--:en-->Swiss Drink<!--:--><!--:de-->Swiss Drink<!--:--><!--:fr-->Swiss Drink<!--:-->', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '73-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 14:01:19', '2013-11-27 14:01:19', '', 73, 'http://localhost/spiralps.ch/uncategorized/73-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
